    {
        "text": "Oh <@UC2A2ARPT> I just got to your mention of Trapdoor (which I’m excited to hear more about!) and was reminded of this bit of the “future work” section of the <https:\/\/youtu.be\/fIEcXAHy6bU?si=mZ-qFm8tvHqpq6yI&t=1507|PANE presentation (25:07)>. I think I’m a bit more skeptical of “values in separate little boxes” than I was back then, though I also think bringing bits of relational visualization into little boxes deserves a lot more exploration.",
